results.content:
The instructor teaches you Parse SDK right from start, how to download the Parse, how to use it. 

He builds a Note taking web app with user login function and user registeration and database saving the notes entered by the user using Parse SDK.

I recommend taking this course if you want to get a quick start on learning and using Parse SDK.
